    {
      "index": 1,
      "start": 0.114,
      "end": 2.459,
      "duration": 2.346,
      "text": "我靠，AI漫剧赛道\n直接他妈大结局了。"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start": 2.734,
      "end": 5.442,
      "duration": 2.708,
      "text": "Gemini three加 gptT\nimages two 的出现，"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start": 5.454,
      "end": 7.589,
      "duration": 2.136,
      "text": "直接宣布了比赛结束。"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start": 7.79,
      "end": 10.849,
      "duration": 3.059,
      "text": "操作简单到我想骂街，\n就把你那破小说往里头一丢，"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start": 11.144,
      "end": 13.456,
      "duration": 2.312,
      "text": "大模型就能自动接管\n一切推理剧情，"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start": 13.771,
      "end": 17.282,
      "duration": 3.512,
      "text": "脚本直接给你生成好，\n不用你费半天劲研究啥复杂提示词，"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start": 17.624,
      "end": 20.5,
      "duration": 2.876,
      "text": "不用你绞尽脑汁\n写什么智能分镜指令，"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start": 20.675,
      "end": 23.65,
      "duration": 2.975,
      "text": "直接给你出连贯到离谱的\n电影级分镜剧本。"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start": 24.148,
      "end": 25.018,
      "duration": 0.87,
      "text": "最牛逼的来了，"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start": 25.303,
      "end": 28.785,
      "duration": 3.481,
      "text": "他直接把人物不一致的\n千古难题给干碎了。"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start": 29.229,
      "end": 32.013,
      "duration": 2.784,
      "text": "一键出人物三视图场景，\n全套道具。"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start": 32.357,
      "end": 34.868,
      "duration": 2.511,
      "text": "你家主角从片头到片尾\n长得半毛钱，"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start": 35.117,
      "end": 35.815,
      "duration": 0.698,
      "text": "不带差的，"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start": 35.924,
      "end": 37.575,
      "duration": 1.65,
      "text": "想换画风，一键搞定。"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start": 38.192,
      "end": 39.272,
      "duration": 1.08,
      "text": "古风赛露露。"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start": 39.671,
      "end": 43.404,
      "duration": 3.733,
      "text": "国风3D日系动漫，啥风格都有，\n做完直接一键导出成片，"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start": 43.788,
      "end": 44.903,
      "duration": 1.115,
      "text": "全程云端运行，"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start": 45.257,
      "end": 46.656,
      "duration": 1.398,
      "text": "半毛钱不吃你电脑配置，"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start": 46.919,
      "end": 47.366,
      "duration": 0.447,
      "text": "就问你，"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start": 47.598,
      "end": 48.651,
      "duration": 1.053,
      "text": "这成品够不够顶？"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start": 49.052,
      "end": 50.238,
      "duration": 1.186,
      "text": "别 time"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start": 50.566,
      "end": 51.567,
      "duration": 1.002,
      "text": "追着我要工具了，"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start": 51.885,
      "end": 52.889,
      "duration": 1.004,
      "text": "我全给你们整理好了，"
